26
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,100
yet you still think of me.

27
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:56,500
I'm very grateful.

28
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:57,700
Enough talk.

29
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:00,180
The fact that you dare

30
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:01,980
to show up in front of me

31
