206
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,500
You take us there.

207
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,340
If you don't want to die,

208
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,060
open the passage quickly

209
00:10:05,140 --> 00:10:06,020
and take us there.

210
